1. *Sledećeg* meseca smo planirali da putujemo. (Next month we planned to travel.)
2. Ona je sastavila svoju plan za *sledeću* nedelju. (She created her plan for the next week.) 
3. Božić će biti *sledećeg* petka. (Christmas will be next Friday.)
4. Zgrada je izgrađena u *sledećem* veku. (The building was constructed in the next century.)
5. On je počeo svoj posao *sledeće* godine. (He started his job the next year.)
6. *Sledećim* putem je stigao do svoje kuće. (He arrived at his house by the next route.)